{
  "stem": "19111.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of the cooking, I must say it was the housemaid, under the supervision and instructions of my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- because my mother ran the business and she couldn't always do that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my sister, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She would do that voluntarily, here and there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, she took great pride when I was a little boy to get up on a stool and cook some breakfast for me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember eggs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Made fried eggs for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, the-- my mother or the housemaid, she used to stand from afar and check it out and make sure that she doesn't get hurt or do any kind of harm.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was so wonderful-- it was my only sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, like all siblings, there were times where we had a run-in with each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes-- I recall the time when my father brought a bicycle, the first bicycle for my sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He brought it at summertime in the resort area there in-- in Niemenczyn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was called Niemenczyn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Outside of the city.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's a difficult one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I'll try.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "N-I-E-M-E-N-C-H-Y-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Niemenczyn.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It is still an-- I understand, a resort area, big resort area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he brought a bicycle there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she wouldn't let me ride the bicycle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wanted-- I was dying to get on the bicycle, learn how to ride it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so things like that, among siblings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We used to argue and fight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She finally put a lock on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my mother pleaded with her to allow me to ride.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my mother put a lock on, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the bicycle stood there for [LAUGHS] a week or so with two locks on.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
